    "Ethical ConcernsThe ethical dimensions surrounding the deployment of chatbots in medical settings demand careful consideration.",
    "Issues such as transparency in chatbot interactions, consent for data usage, and the potential impact on the patient-doctor relationship need thorough examination [8].",
